parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag to deploy in a crash can result in serious injury or death to the vehicle occupants.
symptoms: The airbag did not deploy in a crash
the airbag deployed but did not function properly
the airbag deployed with excessive force
or the airbag deployed with a powdery substance and metal fragments.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The delay in repairing the airbag recall can result in the vehicle being driven without a functioning airbag, increasing the risk of injury or death in a crash.
symptoms: The vehicle owner received a recall notice but the repair parts were not available
the dealer did not have the parts to repair the vehicle
or the manufacturer did not provide a timeline for the repair.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clockspring can cause the airbag to malfunction, leading to serious injury or death in a crash.
symptoms: The airbag light is on
the cruise control and horn are inoperable
or the clockspring is faulty.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the fuel inertia switch can cause the engine to stall or shut off without warning, leading to a loss of power steering and power brakes, which can increase the risk of accidents, especially at high speeds.
symptoms: The engine stalls or shuts off without warning
loss of power steering
loss of power brakes
the vehicle may not restart
the fuel pump may not function
and the vehicle may experience repeated stalling.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The rust and corrosion of the frame can cause the leaf spring shackles to break, leading to loss of control and potential accidents. Additionally, the spare tire can fall off, posing a hazard to other drivers.
symptoms: Rust holes in the frame
leaf spring shackles breaking
spare tire falling off
loud bangs while driving
and vibration in the rear end of the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the leaf spring shackle can cause the spare tire to fall off, leading to loss of control and potential accidents.
symptoms: Leaf spring shackle breaking
spare tire falling off
loud bangs while driving
and vibration in the rear end of the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The corrosion of the brake lines can cause brake failure, leading to loss of control and potential accidents.
symptoms: Brake lines corroding
brake failure
and vibration in the rear end of the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag to deploy in a crash can lead to serious injury or death.
symptoms: Airbag failure to deploy in a crash
resulting in injuries.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the front wheel bearing can cause loss of control and potential accidents.
symptoms: Front wheel bearing failure
vibration in the front end of the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The improper mounting of the swaybar can cause loss of control and potential accidents.
symptoms: Swaybar mounting issue
vibration in the rear end of the vehicle.
